{"tid":194650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港60-80年代科技強到你唔信","createTime":"2017-04-10T06:26:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T01:56:27.000Z","uid":30561,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d1bebbbf53cac3015b52601b452a13eb82a5ff41","tid":194650,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T06:26:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港60-80年代科技強到你唔信:</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當年中國未開放改革，香港電子科技一直亞洲第一，日本都係第二，香港1980年代初製造業鼎盛時期。<br />\n香港電子業的發展屬技術層面最高，初期主要以組裝電視機、音響設備、收音機等家用電器為主。<br />\n其後也開始代工印刷電路板、電腦晶片等業務。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後係金融，造船業，轉口貿易，飲食業，紡織業，製衣業，玩具業，塑膠業，鐘錶業，印刷出版業，旅遊，化妝品業，遠程通訊和光學領域，海水化淡技術，醫藥/製藥業，食品業，制漆業，化妝品業，制帽業，潛艇部件，電視，音樂，建材業，黃埔船塢建造砲艇...等等，<br />\n<br />\n香港70年代係亞洲最早研究電腦RAM既地方，本來英國計劃將香港發生成亞洲硅谷，但因為要回歸所以放棄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現在香港對比一下瑞典。<br />\n<br />\n瑞典GDP第15名,香港GDP第11名<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n瑞典九百九十萬人,香港七百三十萬人 <br />\n瑞典GDP第15名,香港GDP第11名 <br />\n香港清潔工萬零蚊一個月,瑞典就三萬三千蚊一個月 <br />\n堅尼系數香港53.7, 瑞典只係25.4 足足兩倍 <br />\n瑞典發展信息、通訊、生物、醫藥、環保、航空業、核工業、汽車製造業、軍事工業，電訊業和醫藥研究。在軟體開發、微電子、遠程通訊和光子領域。樣樣都世界領先地位。 <br />\n而香港: 金融,地產,飲食業<br />\n<br />\n請睇番南韓台灣同星州，冇天然資源，但科技領域都有不少領先領域。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UnkY4GHH0uo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUnkY4GHH0uo&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=1a76a1ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UnkY4GHH0uo</a>"},{"pid":"be15e5a3c35118315b9f362386809837f7439dea","tid":194650,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T06:33:17.000Z","msg":"香港60-80年代對比一下星州，台灣，包括亞洲多國，香港科技係當勁。"},{"pid":"3a44881e181e66b27f8598edf330a93af81cc145","tid":194650,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T06:35:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港60-80年代對比一下星州，台灣，包括亞洲多國，香港當年既科技係<span style=\"color: red;\">相當勁</span>。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"7c25e51a2a7a651f81ca52648415913e1b2e0cbc","tid":194650,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T06:36:17.000Z","msg":"五毛負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51f77959f20a5af2c86d35da17dc745367b08a43","tid":194650,"uid":45840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T06:36:49.000Z","msg":"同宜家係冇得比既，冇得比較"},{"pid":"b80a61b84f2152dea511004b3be0ce5cc5f19dba","tid":194650,"uid":22580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T06:37:18.000Z","msg":"因為果陣有譚詠麟"},{"pid":"5693c9c425b7f2f888d10c75e6ee03d28b23e02a","tid":194650,"uid":3659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T06:37:21.000Z","msg":"若果香港當年可以成功做到自治領再獨立，<br />\n香港應該係國際上有更高嘅地位"},{"pid":"e50cfbb678430878094a2c22e2c9c97ac31764f3","tid":194650,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T06:38:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為果陣有譚詠麟</blockquote><br />\n唔記得邊個講過同一句說話<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fef5faf1d2450d6c075a54d390d137f7e0e93cce","tid":194650,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T06:41:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5d255f02b6339f3d0d2955a3cc9266a52a4c6bb","tid":194650,"uid":22580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T06:42:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>因為果陣有譚詠麟</blockquote><br />\n唔記得邊個講過同一句說話<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nMe"},{"pid":"de5c29b5d9bb299b471a2cf2860a58034458ae87","tid":194650,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T06:42:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>若果香港當年可以成功做到自治領再獨立，<br />\n香港應該係國際上有更高嘅地位</blockquote><br />\n但當年冇肯人搞"},{"pid":"18870cb64355ba9e30622d2e31ee888d21d77b77","tid":194650,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T06:42:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>因為果陣有譚詠麟</blockquote><br />\n唔記得邊個講過同一句說話<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nMe</blockquote><br />\n譚詠麟一出現香港科技就走下坡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1af5ae2bb984abe14f9921403d79b96d7877c914","tid":194650,"uid":22580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T06:45:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>因為果陣有譚詠麟</blockquote><br />\n唔記得邊個講過同一句說話<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nMe</blockquote><br />\n譚詠麟一出現香港科技就走下坡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n譚詠麟出道帶動香港經濟"},{"pid":"7d928e9bccf9432d22220ab2dbf348ec502eb51d","tid":194650,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T06:46:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>因為果陣有譚詠麟</blockquote><br />\n唔記得邊個講過同一句說話<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nMe</blockquote><br />\n譚詠麟一出現香港科技就走下坡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n譚詠麟出道帶動香港經濟<span style=\"color: red;\">一體化只有金融服務業</span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"96ff976cda2dff16e0db93158853507611bf83d5","tid":194650,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T06:47:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同宜家係冇得比既，冇得比較</blockquote><br />\n因為中國？"},{"pid":"6d4ee864927446346181ab288c2ac0aebdd0bfc1","tid":194650,"uid":22580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T06:48:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>因為果陣有譚詠麟</blockquote><br />\n唔記得邊個講過同一句說話<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nMe</blockquote><br />\n譚詠麟一出現香港科技就走下坡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n譚詠麟出道帶動香港經濟<span style=\"color: red;\">一體化只有金融服務業</span></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n香港果陣咁發達個個魚廁撈飯都係因為校長"},{"pid":"082017156232e13bbbc7bbd0a1fcd7f10204116a","tid":194650,"uid":22580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T06:48:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同宜家係冇得比既，冇得比較</blockquote><br />\n因為中國？</blockquote><br />\n因為譚詠麟冇再囉獎"},{"pid":"68c4fa36811ae76fd5ab7303f8be8f8ce9eadab2","tid":194650,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T06:55:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>因為果陣有譚詠麟</blockquote><br />\n唔記得邊個講過同一句說話<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nMe</blockquote><br />\n譚詠麟一出現香港科技就走下坡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n譚詠麟出道帶動香港經濟<span style=\"color: red;\">一體化只有金融服務業</span></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n香港果陣咁發達個個<span style=\"color: red;\">魚廁</span>撈飯都係因為校長</blockquote><br />\n不了"},{"pid":"5767019c4b2e55ef08392f24a7ba360c56b70d3c","tid":194650,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T06:57:45.000Z","msg":"香港以前有咩R&amp;D公司<br />\n<br />\n而家佢地去哂邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bce99f42fda5b8a8fd8ad8a96ae3291594066a00","tid":194650,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T06:59:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港以前有咩R&amp;D公司<br />\n<br />\n而家佢地去哂邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nVtech<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f5bd50aff8013c557d1c62d5b12d33042866ce4","tid":194650,"uid":80198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T07:04:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港以前有咩R&amp;D公司<br />\n<br />\n而家佢地去哂邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nVtech<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港仲有唔少高質小型高科技公司<br />\n<br />\n不過同深圳華為、比亞迪級數肯定冇得比"},{"pid":"28a4594b245c81acceb5c54c5c21a9f38f4bda0e","tid":194650,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T07:07:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">當年香港60-70年代好多方面既科技，都比起中國，印度，泰國，台灣，韓國，星洲強，以及亞洲多國強</span>。<br />\n<br />\n香港電子業，電腦晶片科技，電路板技術，金融科技，海水化淡技術，印刷技術，鐘錶技術，製衣業技術，電視制作技術，遠程通訊和光學領域，製藥業科技，食品技術。<br />\n<br />\n以上全部都係領先以上多個亞洲國家，或屬技術層面最高。</span></span>"},{"pid":"b1027570d7da747d648c7c6b827bba00608c9ae7","tid":194650,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T07:08:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>香港以前有咩R&amp;D公司<br />\n<br />\n而家佢地去哂邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nVtech<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港仲有唔少高質小型高科技公司<br />\n<br />\n不過同深圳華為、比亞迪級數肯定冇得比</blockquote><br />\n90年代出過快譯通（與強國合作研發薄型電子辭典暨手帳）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba696ac2351ec36d026b7397c53f3267ccf3a71c","tid":194650,"uid":79945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T07:15:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>香港以前有咩R&amp;D公司<br />\n<br />\n而家佢地去哂邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nVtech<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港仲有唔少高質小型高科技公司<br />\n<br />\n不過同深圳華為、比亞迪級數肯定冇得比</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢兩間公司咩級數？垃圾級數？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d014dce29709bd50d68f6ae30ec3e67d400d7ee","tid":194650,"uid":80198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T07:18:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>香港以前有咩R&amp;D公司<br />\n<br />\n而家佢地去哂邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nVtech<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港仲有唔少高質小型高科技公司<br />\n<br />\n不過同深圳華為、比亞迪級數肯定冇得比</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢兩間公司咩級數？垃圾級數？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港人係時候醒下，人地華為已經係日立索尼果個級數嘅公司<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.technews.tw/2017/03/31/huawei-2016/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.technews.tw%2F2017%2F03%2F31%2Fhuawei-2016%2F&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=c9156477\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://finance.technews.tw/2017/03/31/huawei-2016/</a><br />\n<br />\n中國華為 2016 年營收成長逾 3 成，手機銷售全年超過 1.39 億支<br />\n<br />\n中國手機廠商華為（HUAWEI）於 31 日公布 2016 年度財報。根據財報顯示，華為在電信運營商、企業，以及終端設備等三大業務的營收，2016 年全球銷售收入為人民幣 5,216 億元（約新台幣 2.297 兆元），較 2015 年成長 32%。淨利潤為人民幣 371 億元（約新台幣 1,634.2 億元），較 2015 年成長 0.4%。<br />\n<br />\n在投資者最關心的終端設備業務上表現，其中，華為全年智慧型手機的出貨量達到 1.39 億支，相當於每天出貨達到 38 萬支的數量，總銷售金額也達到人民幣 1,798 億元（約新台幣 7,920 億元），較 2016 年成長 44%。<br />\n<br />\n整體來看，華為 2016 年在投入研發的金額上為人民幣 764 億元 （約新台幣 3,365.3 億元）。而 2016 年的整體利潤率從 2015 年的 9.3%，下滑至 7.1%。<br />\n<br />\n就財報所公布的區域營收分析，美洲市場收入佔其華為總收入的 8%，中國則達到 45%，至於歐洲、中東和非洲則佔有近三分之一。"}]}